INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('1','1','Can I Trust Lightinthebox?','If you have any doubts about importing from China, you\'re right to be cautious. Here\'s some key information about Lightinthebox to give you more confidence in starting out with your new China Wholesale supplier:\r\n\r\nLightinthebox is a wholesaler , based in the city of Beijing in Mainland China. Goods are shipped to worldwide by air freight and couriers such as DHL and UPS.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat makes Lightinthebox different from other Chinese suppliers?\r\n\r\n-Unlike most Chinese export companies, there is no minimum order restriction. You can buy products in any order quantity - even 1 piece samples - from a wide selection of the latest released products. So you can test products and find out about the details of importing from Lightinthebox before you\'re committed to any large orders;\r\n\r\n-You can pay by credit card through Paypal, which offers total buyer protection and avoids having to share any of your financial information;\r\n\r\n-Dropshippers can send single items directly from Lightinthebox to their customers.\r\n\r\n-All the products you buy from Lightinthebox are covered by a 12 month guarantee, and are carefully inspected for quality before packing - which is one additional level of QA over and above what is done in the factory;\r\n\r\n-You\'re supported by friendly English speaking staff before and after placing an order, and you can get full product information and support even before purchasing;\r\n\r\n-Your goods are packed carefully, and the packages are correctly labelled and accompanied by all the paperwork that\'s needed for smooth clearance through your country\'s Customs.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhy you can trust Lightinthebox:\r\n\r\n-When you pay for orders on Lightinthebox you do not need to share any of your confidential financial details with Lightinthebox and you\'re protected by Paypal\'s money back guarantees;\r\n\r\n-Lightinthebox Wholesale Ltd is an officially registered company in Hong Kong;\r\n\r\n-The Lightinthebox website is certified \"Hacker Safe\" by Scanalert and is also verified by ValidatedSite.\r\n\r\n\r\nContacting Lightinthebox:\r\n\r\n- http://help.lightinthebox.com/ to view FAQs and submit help tickets (we aim to answer all tickets within 1 working days)\r\n- By phone: 1-650-384-0897 (US) ,you can call us anytime from monday to friday,14:00-08:00 GMT 8+ on saturday and sunday\r\n- you can also email cs@Lightinthebox.com directly','hi, Thks','www.baidu.com','','','','70')
INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('2','1','Does Lightinthebox Has MOQ?','Lightinthebox has no minimum order quantity, and we can ship single item samples or large orders worldwide.','','','','','0','9')
INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('3','1','Can An Order Be Made Without Using The Website?','<p>We prefer our customers to order through our website. You can place orders directly for the products you like.   However, if you want to order in other ways, or have questions about ordering, please contact our customer service representatives by live chat or call us at: 1-650-384-0897 (US)</p>','','','','','0','20')
INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('4','1','What If I Am Making A Large / Bulk Order?','We will provide you with personal customer service for large volume wholesale orders and discuss the shipping options fully.\r\n\r\nFor large volume order quotation,our VIP Customer Manager wish to serve you:\r\n\r\nMSN:\r\nJack@lightinthebox.com\r\nsarah@lightinthebox.com\r\n\r\nEmail:\r\nsales@lightinthebox.com(Sales Department)\r\nJack@lightinthebox.com\r\nsarah@lightinthebox.com','','','','','0','23')
INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('5','1','If I Order Products From Lightinthebox, How To Ship Them To Me?','\"If I order products from Lightinthebox, how to ship them to me? How much is the delivery?How can I trace my order?\r\n\r\nLightinthebox currently ships small and medium sized orders by international couriers.\r\n\r\nThe shipping rates can be previewed inside the Lightinthebox online shop system. On the products page,you just need to click on the \"Estimate Shipping Costs\",and then choose the country you want to ship to,Shipping fee will be estimated by system automaticly.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n*How can I trace my order?\r\n\r\nOnce your order is shipped, you will receive an email from us. In this email, there should be tracking information for your packages as well as the website in which you could trace your order.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n*How Long Will It Take To Delivery?\r\n\r\nTotal delivery time is composed of two parts. The first part is the processing time.This is the time from when your payment is received to when we gather up all the items and pack them. The second part is the actual shipping time. This is the time that it takes for the package to be delivered by the couriers to the destination. Standard shipping normally takes 7-10 days, and express shipping normally takes 2-4 days. Processing takes 1-2 days normally.\r\n\r\n\r\n* Are the packages insured?\r\nShipping with couriers is insured and trackable online. Once your goods are sent out we will email you with a tracking number so you can trace your delivery.\r\n\r\nWhen you checkour your order,you can Add Shipping Insurance to your order .............................................. US$ 1.99\r\n\r\nWe offer Shipping Insurance US$ 1.99 to protect your package against any lost or damaged shipments. Any missing issues reported, we will reship your order immediately.','','','','','0','10')
INSERT INTO faqs_description VALUES('6','1','Payment Methods Accepted','<div class=\"part7_part3\">There are three ways in which you can pay for your Lightinthebox.com orders:<br /> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>PayPal </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Western Union </strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Wire Transfer</strong><br /> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4\"><br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text12 text_bold\"><strong>Paying with PayPal</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text11\"><ol>\r\n<li>With PayPal, you can send payment quickly and securely online. </li>\r\n<li>Through PayPal, you can pay with credit card, debit card, or bank account balance. </li>\r\n<li>Once your order is submitted, you will be redirected to PayPal\'s site where you could make the payment. </li>\r\n</ol></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text11\">Advantages with using PayPal:</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part3\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Payment is traceable. You can trace the status of your payment using your PayPal account. </li>\r\n<li>Payment 	does not require you to use your credit card online (you can transfer 	directly from your bank account). Lightinthebox doesn\'t see your credit 	card number (it is safely encrypted through PayPal\'s server), which 	limits the risk of unauthorized use. </li>\r\n<li>The location the seller is shipping to (also call the destination country or region).<br /> <br /> <br /> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text12 text_bold\"><strong>Paying with Western Union:</strong><br /> <br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text11\">We are also happy to accept Western Union payment for most orders. Due to the timeliness and convenience of the payment for us, we offer a 7% discount to the total of your order (shipping included).</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text11\">For Western Union payments</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part3\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Beneficiary: MEI LI </li>\r\n<li>First Name: MEI </li>\r\n<li>Last Name: LI </li>\r\n<li>Country: CHINA </li>\r\n<li>Address: Room 717, Huaheng Tower, Xidan, Xicheng District, Beijing, PR China, 100032 </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4\"><span class=\"text_bold\">IMPORTANT NOTICE</span>: Please email your ORDER NUMBER, WESTERN UNION CONTROL NUMBER, ORDER AMOUNT, SENDER\'S FIRST and LAST NAME, SENDER\'S ADDRESS and COUNTRY, and SENDER\'S PHONE NUMBER to: westernunion@lightinthebox.com after you send payment through Western Union.<br /> <br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text12 text_bold\">Paying with Wire Transfer:</div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part4 text11\">We are also happy to accept Wire Transfer payment for most orders.<br /> <strong><br /> For Wire Transfer payments<br /> <br /> </strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"part7_part3\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Name: Yang Yu </li>\r\n<li>Account Number: 3219508 </li>\r\n<li>Bank Name: China Merchants Bank Hong Kong Branch </li>\r\n<li>Bank Code: 238 </li>\r\n<li>Branch Code: 860 </li>\r\n<li>Swift Code: CMBCHKHH </li>\r\n<li>Bank Address: 21 Floor Bank Of America Tower, 12 Harcourt Road, Central, Hong Kong<br /> <br /> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><span class=\"text_bold\"><strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE</strong></span>: Please email your ORDER NUMBER, ORDER AMOUNT, SENDER\'S FIRST and LAST NAME, SENDER\'S ADDRESS and COUNTRY, and SENDER\'S PHONE NUMBER to:cs@lightinthebox.com after you send payment through Wire Transfer.</div>','','','','','0','4')
